description:

title: Metawatch: Warhammer Age of Sigmar – The 15th of February 2024
description:
The team behind Warhammer Age of Sigmar talk about the new balance updates for the game.

* Please note that at one point in this video we state that Blue and Brimstone Horrors would become Battleline for Disciples of Tzeentch. This was in error – they’ve had their points lowered, but they didn’t become Battleline. The Changer of the Ways is as tricksy as ever! 

Find out more of what's changing in the Mortal Realms: https://ow.ly/T8y650QBhxq
